        <p>Facebook and LinkedIn deliver the highest ROI for most HVAC companies. Facebook excels at reaching homeowners during emergencies, while LinkedIn connects with commercial decision-makers. YouTube offers excellent conversion rates but requires significant video production time that many contractors can't sustain.</p>
        
