        <p>Measuring social media ROI requires tracking both engagement metrics and business outcomes. Use these tools and metrics to evaluate performance:</p>
        
        <h3>Essential Tracking Metrics</h3>
        
        <p><strong>Lead Generation Metrics:</strong><br>
        - Cost per lead by platform<br>
        - Lead-to-customer conversion rate<br>
        - Average customer lifetime value from social leads<br>
        - Response time to social media inquiries</p>
        
        <p><strong>Engagement Quality Metrics:</strong><br>
        - Comments per post (indicates genuine interest)<br>
        - Shares and saves (extends reach organically)<br>
        - Direct messages and phone calls from posts<br>
        - Website traffic from social media referrals</p>
        
