        <p>These three HVAC companies demonstrate different successful approaches to social media marketing:</p>
        
        <h3>Case Study 1: ABC Heating & Air (Phoenix, AZ)</h3>
        
        <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Facebook-focused emergency response marketing<br>
        <strong>Results:</strong> 156% increase in emergency calls, $180,000 additional annual revenue<br>
        <strong>Key Tactics:</strong> Posted real-time emergency responses, used Facebook ads targeting "AC repair" keywords during summer months, responded to comments within 15 minutes during peak seasons</p>
        
