        <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> LinkedIn commercial prospecting combined with educational content<br>
        <strong>Results:</strong> 12 new commercial accounts worth $340,000 annually<br>
        <strong>Key Tactics:</strong> Published weekly articles about commercial HVAC challenges, used Apollo.io to identify property managers, sent personalized connection requests with relevant content</p>
        
