        <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Multi-platform approach with Instagram visual content and Facebook community engagement<br>
        <strong>Results:</strong> 89% increase in residential customers aged 25-45<br>
        <strong>Key Tactics:</strong> Posted time-lapse installation videos, engaged actively in local Facebook groups, ran Instagram contests for free maintenance services</p>
